    "body": "I believe I may have found a workaround for this. While trying to write some custom logic to get this to work with foundry scripting I found that if you run anvil and fork mainnet and then run your script command on that forked network it seems to verify successfully. As a reference here is the command with flags.\r\n\r\n`anvil --fork-url $MAINNET_RPC`\r\n\r\n`forge script script/Test.s.sol:TestScript --fork-url http://localhost:8545 --verifier-url http://localhost:3000/api/verify --etherscan-api-key blacksmith --broadcast --verify -vvvv`\r\n\r\nThe UI does seem to work as well but havent done a lot of testing.",
